&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructional Oversight &amp;amp; Curriculum&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supervise and mentor DP Empowered Faculty across schools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and refine all instructional materials and curriculum frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide ongoing professional development for DP Empowered Faculty&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure consistent pedagogical approach and academic standards across all schools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
