&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Foster a life of active citizenship for all scholars through the implementation of age-appropriate conversations and activities centered on current events, participation in community service and outreach opportunities, and active celebration of scholars&#39; culture, heritage, and identity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Engage in whole-school events and tasks, including transitions, family conferences, tutoring, and other activities/duties.&lt;/li&gt;
