&lt;li&gt;Experienced Organizer: Experience in community organizing, marketing, and charter school student recruiting is preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organized and Strategic: You utilize your subject-matter expertise to engage with prospective parents and scholars and partner with teams, schools, and others to maximize new student enrollment.&lt;/li&gt;
